    <string name="ui_screen_privacy_first_text">Five points worth reading. :sunglasses:</string>
    <string name="ui_screen_privacy_second_text">1. The data you enter is visible to Aura users around you.
        \n\n2. No data is sent over the internet.
        \n\n3. We don\'t collect any data.
        \n\n4. Aura is and will remain free
        \n\n5. Aura believes in humanism, freedom of speech, respect and equality of all people. If you don\'t, please uninstall it and read a wide variety of books.
